/ CHROMEBOOK POWERWASH METHOD \

How to powerwash a district restricted chromebook
: Sign out of your Chromebook / Close it and reopen
: Don't sign in instead Press and hold CTRL+ALT+SHIFT+R all at once
: When the prompt comes up click restart
: In the box that appears, click power-wash, then continue
: Then the Chromebook should restart and once it restarts it will be power-washed
: Note this makes the Chromebook unstable and you won't be able to sign in

